            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-11" style="border-left: 4px solid white; border-bottom: 1px solid white; margin: 40px;">
            <h1 style="color: white;">Fullstack Development + api</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4">
            <div class="card" style="border: none;">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="~/img/portfolio/duoBudget.png" alt="Card image cap">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">DuoBudget</h5>
                    <p class="card-text"><strong>Asp.net stack:</strong> An application to share finances with your partner to make financial planning easier</p>
                    <a href="https://duobudget.azurewebsites.net" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="border: none;">Website</a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/kevinnguyen0509/DuoBudget" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: #302f2f; border: none;">github</a>
