            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-4">
            <div class="card" style="border: none;">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="~/img/portfolio/toDuoList.png" alt="Card image cap">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">ToDuoList</h5>
                    <p class="card-text"><strong>Asp.net stack:</strong> An application to share a grocery list with your partner that you can both add and remove from</p>
                    <a href="http://toduolist.azurewebsites.net/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="border: none;">Website</a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/kevinnguyen0509/ToDuoList" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: #302f2f; border: none;">github</a>
