                <h5 class="card-title">Stock calculator</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Worked with an API in order to get raw financial data so I could quickly calculate if its a good stock to research or not.</p>
                    <a href="https://kevinsportfolio.azurewebsites.net/projects/stock-calculator/index.html" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="border: none;">Website</a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/kevinnguyen0509/KevinsPortfolioProjects/tree/master/kevins-portfolio/projects/stock-calculator"  target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: #302f2f; border: none;">github</a>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
