                    <p class="card-text">A project used to sharpen my Javascript skills. Its a guessing game that tells the user if the are close to the correct number.</p>
                    <a href="https://kevinsportfolio.azurewebsites.net/projects/guessMyNumberGame/index.html" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="border: none;">Website</a>
