                        <p class="card-text">A project to recreate the "pig-game" where the user tries to get to 100, but if you roll a 1 its the other player's turn.'</p>
                        <a href="https://kevinsportfolio.azurewebsites.net/projects/pig-game/index.html" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="border: none;">Website</a>
